Kotori is a second-year student at Otonokizaka High School.
%
Kotori is a childhood friend of Honoka and Umi.
%
Kotori is the wardrobe supervisor and designer for μ's.
%
Kotori secretly worked part-time at a maid café in Akihabara as the "Legendary Maid Minalinsky".
%
Kotori's mother is the director of Otonokizaka High School.
%
Kotori is a member of the sub-unit Printemps.
%
Kotori's solo album is titled "Kotori, Lovin' You."
%
Kotori's main color is gray, though she is commonly depicted in green.
